<paragraph blockId="10.[178,1087,890,934]" pageId="10" pageNumber="1341">
T y p e m a t e r i a l: 
<typeStatus box="[433,506,890,910]" pageId="10" pageNumber="1341">Holotype</typeStatus>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[552,636,890,910]" name="Cameroon" pageId="10" pageNumber="1341">Kamerun</collectingCountry>
, Bosum, bei Termiten, leg. Tessmann (MNHUB). 
<typeStatus box="[223,302,914,934]" pageId="10" pageNumber="1341">Paratype</typeStatus>
: 1, same origin (MNHUB).
</paragraph>
